      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Many tieflings born of Hell&rsquo;s fiery depths can call forth flames to sear their foes. The tiefling can cast @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.a2zXJ84rzkD8SIBe]{Overheat} as a spell-like ability. At 11th level, the scion can instead cast @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.WP0QPu6QvApGaQIG]{Explosive Blast} as a spell-like ability. The scion can invoke hellfire this way once per day.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces deceitful and fiendish gloom.</strong></p>\n<p><br /><em>After adding the spell to the Spellbook tab, edit the spell's Details, changing the Spell Preparation Mode to Innate Spellcasting, and change Limited uses to 1 of 1 Day. Use the formula </em><em>(11 + @abilities.cha.mod) in the Saving Throw field for the Overheat spell-like ability. Use the formula </em><em style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">(13 + @abilities.cha.mod) for the Explosive Blast spell-like ability</em><em><br /></em></p>"
